commit.message:
Version the data format.

Closes issue #188.
Switch to footbibliography header for better consistency.
Do not yet document bibtex2 in the readme.
New bibfile module for bibfile related functions.
Make the CiteRole more easy for inheritance.
Rename submodules (to avoid clashes with future other similar functions).

Merge pull request #190 from mcmtroffaes/feature/multiple-footbibliography-directives

Support multiple footbibliography directives in the same document.

commit.message: Get rid of the bibliography cache (since there's no more need for it, all info is stored elsewhere).
Move bibfiles cache to global non-footbib specific variable.
Rename footbib to bibtex2 (plan is to add more parallel safe directives and roles).
Rename config values for more sensible sharing with other future bibtex related directives.
Add configuration error test for coverage.
Clean up, proper test for issue #187.
